## 6. Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology | Why |
|---|---|---|
| Backend language | Python 3.11 | Async support, AI ecosystem |
| Web framework | FastAPI | High-performance async, auto-generates Swagger UI |
| Agent orchestration | LangGraph | Stateful multi-node AI graphs with full audit trails |
| LLM | Claude (Haiku for fast tasks, Sonnet for complex) | Best instruction-following, JSON output reliability |
| Task queue | Celery + Redis | Scheduled jobs, background processing, beat scheduler |
| Primary database | PostgreSQL 15 | ACID compliance, row-level security, UUID support |
| Vector store | Qdrant | Semantic search for agent context retrieval |
| Embeddings | nomic-embed-text via Ollama (CPU) | Open-source, self-hosted, no API cost |
| Event router | n8n (self-hosted) | Webhook intake, workflow automation |
| PDF generation | WeasyPrint + Jinja2 | HTML-to-PDF, full CSS styling |
| Frontend | React 18 + Vite | Fast dev server, component-based |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS | Utility-first, consistent design tokens |
| State management | Zustand | Lightweight, persisted auth state |
| API client | Axios + React Query | Auto-retry, background refetch, optimistic updates |
| Email | Gmail API (OAuth) | Inbound + outbound, reply detection |
| WhatsApp | WATI API | Client-facing messaging |
| Internal alerts | Slack SDK | Team notifications |
| Social scheduling | Buffer REST API | Post scheduling from approval pipeline |
| CRM | HubSpot Python SDK | Lead and deal management |
| Ads data | Meta Marketing API + Google Ads API + GA4 | Campaign performance |
| Infrastructure | Proxmox (self-hosted) | Host VMs on your own hardware |
| Auth | JWT (PyJWT) + bcrypt | Stateless, role-based |

