## 14. Testing Guide

### Testing without any API keys

The entire platform can be tested without a single external API credential. Every integration stubs gracefully:

| Integration | Stub behaviour |
|---|---|
| Gmail | Logs `[GMAIL STUB]` to console, marks message as sent |
| WATI | Logs `[WATI STUB]` to console |
| Slack | Logs `[SLACK STUB]` to console |
| Buffer | Returns fake post ID, marks task as scheduled |
| Meta Ads | Returns realistic sample data |
| Google Ads | Returns realistic sample data |
| GA4 | Returns realistic sample data |
| SerpAPI | Returns realistic stub search results |
| Claude | Requires `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` — no stub for AI features |
| HubSpot | Logs `[HubSpot STUB]` to console |

### End-to-end test flow

Follow this sequence to test every module:

**Preparation (5 minutes):**
```
1. Login as superadmin → create agency with all modules [M1-M11]
2. Login as owner → create a geofence zone (Settings)
3. Create 2 employees
4. Create 3 clients
```

**M1 — Attendance:**
```
