6. Owner → Team → Live Attendance → employee shows as Clocked In
7. Employee → Clock Out
8. Owner → Team → Today's attendance shows session with hours
```

**M1 — Tasks:**
```
9. Owner → create task assigned to employee, set deadline = tomorrow
10. Employee → My Tasks → see task → click "Start Task" → status: in_progress
11. Employee → "Submit for Review" → status: submitted
12. Owner → Tasks → click "Verify" → verified
```

**M1 — Payroll:**
```
13. Owner → Financial → "Run Payroll" → select current month
14. Payroll run created showing calculated pay per employee
15. Owner → "Approve & Generate PDFs"
16. Employee → Payslips → see their payslip → Download PDF
