**M2 — Onboarding:**
```
17. Owner → Clients → click a client → "Trigger Onboarding"
18. Wait ~15 seconds → check onboarding status
19. Should show 4 steps: generate_brief, send_email, update_crm, notify_am
20. client_brief field shows Claude's generated text (requires ANTHROPIC_API_KEY)
```

**M2 — Invoices:**
```
21. Owner → Financial → Invoices → "New Invoice"
